## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ff9bc-104">속성 또는 필드는 공용 이어야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff9bc-104">The property or field must be public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ff9bc-105">속성을 포함 하는 클래스도 표시 되어야 합니다는 <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute> 특성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff9bc-105">The class that contains the property must be marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute> attribute.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="ff9bc-106">모든 필드 또는 클래스에서이 컴퓨터나 다른 WMI 공급자 확장 특성으로 표시 되지 않은 속성 계측 되지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff9bc-106">Any fields or properties in the class that are not marked with this or another WMI Provider Extensions attribute will not be instrumented.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ff9bc-107">다음 예제에서는 속성을 표시 하려면 ManagementConfiguration 특성을 사용 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff9bc-107">The following example shows how to use the ManagementConfiguration attribute to mark a property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ff9bc-108">이 속성은 WMI에 노출 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff9bc-108">This property is exposed to WMI.</span></span>  

```csharp  
// Use the ManagementConfiguration attribute to specify that a property  
// is a read/write property in the provider. Consumers will be  
// able to get and set this property value through WMI.  
[ManagementConfiguration]  
public double ReadableWritableProperty  
{  
    get { return this.propertyValue; }  
    set { this.propertyValue = value; }  
}  
```
